c: 42
v: 5
t: "Mawunde gakusigalaga panandi kuti gapasuchepasuche pachanya pakwe (ligongo lyakun’jogopa Allah), ni Achimalaika akuluswejesyaga lumbili lwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah), ni kwaŵendelaga chikululuko ŵali petaka. Manyililani yanti chisimu Allah ni Jwali Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"